  "detailed_description": "<h1>Update Notes</h1><p>New/Changed Features with Update 1.1:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Point counter at game screen<br></li><li>More shield charges after bosses<br></li><li>Bug-Symbol in \"level selection screen\" to find new ships<br></li><li>Less load time for weapons<br></li><li>Start the game with +5 extra shield</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Space Bugs is a Retro Space Shooter with:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 levels<br><br></li><li>10 different ships<br><br></li><li>each with special skill<br><br></li><li>40 trophies<br><br></li><li>simple control, only by mouse or keyboard</li></ul><br>Take control of the ships and shoot your way through level by level to the final end boss!",
